      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not that simple though. there's no \"adult\" who can make the internet stop or make people stop hating me. it just feels like everyone has already decided who i am and they're never gonna let it go. like no matter how much i try to hide or fix things, the feeling of being watched and judged is just always there. it's exhausting. i feel like i'm just stuck in this loop of misery.",
